  "Say": {
    "_dirName": "Say",
    "_dirType": "sub",
    "0": {
      "_dirName": "0",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Oh, thanks for coming! I just got a new request for you. It seems like #b#p415##k from the hardware store is having trouble sleeping these days. Someone apparently stole his pillow... Now who in their right mind would steal a pillow? Geez."
      },
      "1": {
        "_dirName": "1",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "In any case, we need to make a new pillow, but it's not that easy to get the required materials. Can you get #b20 #t4003002#s and 20 #t4000049#s#k? That shouldn't be too difficult. Come see me after you have collected everything."
      }
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Great work. It is a pleasure working with you, you know that? Alright, let's talk rewards. #b#p415##k is giving you #b1 #t4010100##k and #b1 #t4010101##k."
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Alright, if you need work sometime down the road, feel free to come back and see me."
        }
      },
